ls every day-which adds up to 1.2 million meals, including3 million bananas and 27 tons of coffee.\", \"from\": 8962, \"to\": 9207, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Their diversesportsdemand very different requirements.\", \"from\": 9209, \"to\": 9263, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Some athletes must maintain an exact weight, while others may need to increase their carbohydrate or protein intake.\", \"from\": 9264, \"to\": 9380, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After all,nutrition fuels athletic performance.\", \"from\": 9381, \"to\": 9428, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And yet, some athletes come from places where malnutrition is a constant concern.\", \"from\": 9430, \"to\": 9511, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In many parts of the world, hunger is deeply linked to conflict, which has beenon the rise.\", \"from\": 9512, \"to\": 9603, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"More than117 million peoplewere forcibly displaced last year.\", \"from\": 9604, \"to\": 9665, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It can create a vicious cycle, as many displaced people face hunger and uncertainty.\", \"from\": 9666, \"to\": 9750, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But, their stories do not have to end there.\", \"from\": 9751, \"to\": 9795, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As we prepare to cheer on the Refugee Olympic Team, we are spotlighting accomplished athletes and their countries of origin-all places where Action Against Hunger runs programs that can help the next generation realize their potential.\", \"from\": 9797, \"to\": 10032, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9827, \"end\": 9847, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IOC_Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.999999025354575, \"rank\": 9.746462616026844e-07, \"text\": \"Refugee Olympic Team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IOC_Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IOC_Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Talent is everywhere, and it can become greatness when it is nourished.\", \"from\": 10034, \"to\": 10105, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For proof, look no further than theRefugee Olympic Team.\", \"from\": 10106, \"to\": 10162, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Launched at the 2016 Olympic Games in Rio, the team isa symbol of hope.\", \"from\": 10163, \"to\": 10234, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10201, \"end\": 10204, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999388049839818, \"rank\": 6.119829162944048e-05, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This year, theteam is composed of 37 athletes from 15 National Olympic Committees, competing across 12 sports.\", \"from\": 10235, \"to\": 10345, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10289, \"end\": 10316, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.9999994013580336, \"rank\": 5.986421625362565e-07, \"text\": \"National Olympic Committees\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To be eligible, an athlete must be a top competitor in their sport and a refugee in their host country.\", \"from\": 10346, \"to\": 10449, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Action Against Hunger is familiar with the ongoing global refugee crisis, which hassurgedin recent years.\", \"from\": 10451, \"to\": 10556, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Conflict is a major driving force behind the growing displacement, and more forced displacement equals more hunger-more than85%of people living in conflict-affected countries are experiencing food insecurity.\", \"from\": 10557, \"to\": 10765, \"ent