bout them on your socials.\", \"from\": 14831, \"to\": 14903, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Note the link between nutrition and performance in sports and in life, celebrate the talent that can emerge from hardship, and help bring attention to the tens of millions who still need support.\", \"from\": 14904, \"to\": 15099, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After decades of conflict and growing climate stress,24 million Afghans, or nearly 60% of the population,need help to afford food and other basic necessities.\", \"from\": 15101, \"to\": 15259, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15165, \"end\": 15172, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"score\": 0.9821422157706712, \"rank\": 0.015856275821494712, \"text\": \"Afghans\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Studies have shown that a majority of the population also is dealing with mental health challenges, which can be deeply linked to hunger.\", \"from\": 15260, \"to\": 15397, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A number of athletes originally from Afghanistan are part of the Refugee Olympic Team.\", \"from\": 15399, \"to\": 15485, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15436, \"end\": 15447, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"score\": 0.9999997552909308, \"rank\": 2.447090337729667e-07, \"text\": \"Afghanistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\"}, {\"begin\": 15464, \"end\": 15484, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IOC_Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.999999025354575, \"rank\": 9.746462616026844e-07, \"text\": \"Refugee Olympic Team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IOC_Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IOC_Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2020_S