s\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IOC_Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IOC_Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hunger is manmade, and the solutions can be, too.\", \"from\": 16764, \"to\": 16813, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Together, we can create a world where every life is well nourished.\", \"from\": 16814, \"to\": 16881, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We hope you will join us in showing your support for athletes andrefugeesduring the 2024 Paris Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 16883, \"to\": 16992, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Cheer them on, share their stories, and post about them on your socials.\", \"from\": 16993, \"to\": 17065, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Note the link between nutrition and performance in sports and in life, celebrate the talent that can emerge from hardship, and help bring attention to the tens of millions who still need support.\", \"from\": 17066, \"to\": 17261, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To meet the nutritional needs of 15,000 athletes and staff from208 countries and territories,the 2024 Paris Olympicswill need to prepare 40,000 meals every day-which adds up to 1.2 million meals, including3 million bananas and 27 tons of coffee.\", \"from\": 17263, \"to\": 17508, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Their diversesportsdemand very different requirements.\", \"from\": 17510, \"to\": 17564, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Some athletes must maintain an exact weight, while others may need to increase their carbohydrate or protein intake.\", \"from\": 17565, \"to\": 17681, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After all,nutrition fuels athletic performance.\", \"from\": 17682, \"to\": 17729, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And yet, some athletes come from places where malnutrition is a constant concern.\", \"from\": 17731, \"to\": 17812, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In many parts of the world, hunger is deeply linked to conflict, which has beenon the rise.\", \"from\": 17813, \"to\": 17904, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"More than117 million peoplewere forcibly displaced last year.\", \"from\": 17905, \"to\": 17966, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It can create a vicious cycle, as many displaced people face hunger and uncertainty.\", \"from\": 17967, \"to\": 18051, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But, their stories do not have to end there.\", \"from\": 18052, \"to\": 18096, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As we prepare to cheer on the Refugee Olympic Team, we are spotlighting accomplished athletes and their countries of origin-all places where Action Against Hunger runs programs that can help the next generation realize their potential.\", \"from\": 18098, \"to\": 18333, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 18128, \"end\": 18148, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IOC_Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.999999025354575, \"rank\": 9.746462616026844e-07, \"text\": \"Refugee Olympic Team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IOC_Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IOC_Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Talent is everywhere, and it can become greatness when it is nourished.\", \"from\": 18335, \"to\": 18406, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For proof, look no further than theRefugee Olympic Team.\", \"from\": 18407, \"to\": 18463, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Launched at the 2016 Olympic Games in Rio, the team isa symbol of hope.\", \"from\": 18464, \"to\": 18535, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 18502, \"end\": 18505, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999388049839818, \"rank\": 6.119829162944048e-05, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This year, theteam is composed of 37 athletes from 15 National Olympic Committees, competing across 12 sports.\", \"from\": 18536, \"to\": 18646, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 18590, \"end\": 18617, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.9999994013580336, \"rank\": 5.986421625362565e-07, \"text\": \"National Olympic Committees\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To be eligible, an athlete must be a top competitor in their sport and a refugee in their host country.\", \"from\": 18647, \"to\": 18750, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Action Against Hunger is familiar with the ongoing global refugee crisis, which hassurgedin recent years.\", \"from\": 18752, \"to\": 18857, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Conflict is a major driving force behind the growing displacement, and more forced displacement equals more hunger-more than85%of people living in conflict-affected countries are experiencing food insecurity.\", \"from\": 18858, \"to\": 19066, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As we prepare to cheer on the Refugee Olympic Team, we are spotlighting accomplished athletes and their countries of origin-all places where Action Against Hunger runs programs that can help the next generation realize their potential.\", \"from\": 19068, \"to\": 19303, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19098, \"end\": 19118, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IOC_Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.999999025354575, \"rank\": 9.746462616026844e-07, \"text\": \"Refugee Olympic Team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IOC_Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IOC_Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"AfghanistanAfter decades of conflict and growing climate stress,24 million Afghans, or nearly 60% of the population,need help to afford food and other basic necessities.\", \"from\": 19305, \"to\": 19474, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19380, \"end\": 19387, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"score\": 0.9821422157706712, \"rank\": 0.015856275821494712, \"text\": \"Afghans\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Studies have shown that a majority of the population also is dealing with mental health challenges, which can be deeply linked to hunger.A number of athletes originally from Afghanistan are part of the Refugee Olympic Team.\", \"from\": 19475, \"to\": 19698, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19649, \"end\": 19660, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"score\": 0.9999997552909308, \"rank\": 2.447090337729667e-07, \"text\": \"Afghanistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\"}, {\"begin\": 19677, \"end\": 19697, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IOC_Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.999999025354575, \"rank\": 9.746462616026844e-07, \"text\": \"Refugee Olympic Team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IOC_Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IOC_Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We will be rooting for them:Manizha Talashis a breakdancer who now resides inSpainbut has been reunited with members of her hip-hop community from Kabul.Farzad Mansouri's sport is taekwondo.\", \"from\": 19699, \"to\": 19889, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19727, \"end\": 19734, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manizha\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"tex